{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/[locale]/layout,_N_T_/[locale]/politique-de-confidentialite/layout,_N_T_/[locale]/politique-de-confidentialite/page,_N_T_/fr/politique-de-confidentialite"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--W36t2dCKYZcniARoIPLff--><html lang=\"fr\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" imageSrcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/cc6076e0af990590.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-417084e9e055685a.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-c023c6e3521b1417.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/255-38b49df12a94ee57.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-ce6b2ea84b9aaf60.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/850-3779ccbb4ebfcae5.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/%5Blocale%5D/layout-66ea3f57ca5f148e.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/%5Blocale%5D/politique-de-confidentialite/page-6cbdc078e3e79f4a.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>Politique de confidentialité – SRD Partners Sàrl | SRD Partners</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Informations sur la protection de vos données personnelles conformément à la nLPD suisse.\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://www.srdpartners.ch/fr\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"fr\" href=\"https://www.srdpartners.ch/fr\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"en\" href=\"https://www.srdpartners.ch/en\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"pt\" href=\"https://www.srdpartners.ch/pt\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"x-default\" href=\"https://www.srdpartners.ch/fr\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Politique de confidentialité – SRD Partners Sàrl | SRD Partners\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Informations sur la protection de vos données personnelles conformément à la nLPD suisse.\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"SRD Partners Sàrl\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"fr_CH\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Politique de confidentialité – SRD Partners Sàrl | SRD Partners\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Informations sur la protection de vos données personnelles conformément à la nLPD suisse.\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"__variable_ea5885 __variable_ccfcb5 font-body antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FinancialService\",\"name\":\"SRD Partners Sàrl\",\"url\":\"https://www.srdpartners.ch\",\"telephone\":\"+41328572419\",\"email\":\"cremilde.hirschi@srdpartners.ch\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"streetAddress\":\"Les Vernets 2\",\"postalCode\":\"2035\",\"addressLocality\":\"Corcelles-NE\",\"addressCountry\":\"CH\"}}</script><header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-white transition-shadow duration-200 border-b border-black/[0.06]\"><div class=\"container-main\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between transition-all duration-300 h-20 sm:h-24\"><a class=\"flex items-center shrink-0 group focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded\" aria-label=\"SRD Partners Sàrl\" href=\"/fr\"><div class=\"px-2 py-1 transition-opacity duration-200 group-hover:opacity-75\"><img alt=\"SRD Partners Sàrl\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-auto transition-all duration-300 h-12\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></a><nav aria-label=\"Navigation principale\" class=\"hidden md:flex items-center\"><ul class=\"flex items-center gap-0.5\"><li><a class=\"relative flex items-center px-4 py-2.5 font-body text-sm rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-ink hover:text-gold\" href=\"/fr\">Accueil</a></li><li><button type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-2.5 font-body text-sm rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-ink hover:text-gold\">Services<svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\"></polyline></svg></button></li><li><a class=\"relative flex items-center px-4 py-2.5 font-body text-sm rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-ink hover:text-gold\" href=\"/fr/qui-sommes-nous\">Qui sommes-nous</a></li><li><a class=\"relative flex items-center px-4 py-2.5 font-body text-sm rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-ink hover:text-gold\" href=\"/fr/contact\">Contact</a></li></ul></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\" aria-label=\"Language selector\"><span class=\"flex items-center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"font-body text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wider transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded px-0.5 text-gold\" aria-pressed=\"true\">FR</button><span class=\"mx-1 text-[11px] text-black/15\" aria-hidden=\"true\">|</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"font-body text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wider transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded px-0.5 text-ink/35 hover:text-ink\" aria-pressed=\"false\">EN</button><span class=\"mx-1 text-[11px] text-black/15\" aria-hidden=\"true\">|</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"font-body text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wider transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded px-0.5 text-ink/35 hover:text-ink\" aria-pressed=\"false\">PT</button></span></div><a class=\"hidden sm:inline-flex btn-primary text-xs py-2.5 px-5\" href=\"/fr/contact\">Demander une offre</a><button type=\"button\" class=\"md:hidden inline-flex items-center justify-center w-9 h-9 rounded text-ink hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" aria-label=\"Ouvrir le menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-menu\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute left-0 right-0 top-full bg-white border-t border-black/[0.05] shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(26,10,40,0.10)] transition-all duration-[180ms] ease-smooth opacity-0 -translate-y-2 pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"container-main py-8 grid gap-8 grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_260px]\"><div><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] font-semibold text-muted tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-4 px-3\">Finances &amp; Fiscalité</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-0.5\"><li><a class=\"group flex flex-col px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/comptabilite-fiscalite\"><span class=\"font-body text-[13.5px] font-medium text-ink group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150\">Comptabilité &amp; Fiscalité</span><span class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5 leading-relaxed\">Tenue des comptes, déclarations TVA et optimisation fiscale.</span></a></li><li><a class=\"group flex flex-col px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/ressources-humaines\"><span class=\"font-body text-[13.5px] font-medium text-ink group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150\">Ressources Humaines</span><span class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5 leading-relaxed\">Fiches de paie, déclarations sociales et conseil RH.</span></a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] font-semibold text-muted tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-4 px-3\">Administration &amp; Immobilier</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-0.5\"><li><a class=\"group flex flex-col px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/gestion-administrative\"><span class=\"font-body text-[13.5px] font-medium text-ink group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150\">Gestion administrative</span><span class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5 leading-relaxed\">Facturation, suivi des flux et domiciliation d&#x27;entreprise.</span></a></li><li><a class=\"group flex flex-col px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/gestion-immobiliere\"><span class=\"font-body text-[13.5px] font-medium text-ink group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150\">Gestion Immobilière</span><span class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5 leading-relaxed\">Gestion locative, suivi financier et accompagnement juridique.</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[180px]\"><div><p class=\"font-display text-[17px] font-semibold text-navy mb-2.5 leading-snug\">Tous nos services</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed\">Un accompagnement complet pour chaque dimension de votre entreprise.</p></div><a class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-body text-[13px] font-semibold text-gold hover:gap-2.5 transition-all duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded\" href=\"/fr/services\">Voir les services<svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div></div></div><div id=\"mobile-menu\" class=\"md:hidden absolute left-0 right-0 top-full bg-white border-t border-black/[0.06] transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden max-h-0 opacity-0 pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><nav aria-label=\"Navigation mobile\"><ul class=\"container-main pt-3 pb-6 flex flex-col\"><li class=\"border-b border-black/[0.05] last:border-0\"><a class=\"flex items-center px-1 py-3.5 font-body text-sm font-medium rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-ink hover:text-gold\" href=\"/fr\">Accueil</a></li><li class=\"border-b border-black/[0.05] last:border-0\"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-3 px-1 py-3.5 font-body text-sm font-medium text-ink transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded\">Services<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 text-muted/50 rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\"></polyline></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-3 space-y-4\"><div><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] font-semibold text-muted tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-1.5 px-1\">Finances &amp; Fiscalité</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col\"><li><a class=\"block px-3 py-2.5 font-body text-sm text-ink hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150 rounded focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/comptabilite-fiscalite\">Comptabilité &amp; Fiscalité</a></li><li><a class=\"block px-3 py-2.5 font-body text-sm text-ink hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150 rounded focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/ressources-humaines\">Ressources Humaines</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] font-semibold text-muted tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-1.5 px-1\">Administration &amp; Immobilier</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col\"><li><a class=\"block px-3 py-2.5 font-body text-sm text-ink hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150 rounded focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/gestion-administrative\">Gestion administrative</a></li><li><a class=\"block px-3 py-2.5 font-body text-sm text-ink hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150 rounded focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/gestion-immobiliere\">Gestion Immobilière</a></li></ul></div></div></div></li><li class=\"border-b border-black/[0.05] last:border-0\"><a class=\"flex items-center px-1 py-3.5 font-body text-sm font-medium rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-ink hover:text-gold\" href=\"/fr/qui-sommes-nous\">Qui sommes-nous</a></li><li class=\"border-b border-black/[0.05] last:border-0\"><a class=\"flex items-center px-1 py-3.5 font-body text-sm font-medium rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-ink hover:text-gold\" href=\"/fr/contact\">Contact</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mt-3 pt-4 border-t border-black/[0.06] px-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\" aria-label=\"Language selector\"><span class=\"flex items-center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"font-body text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wider transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded px-0.5 text-gold\" aria-pressed=\"true\">FR</button><span class=\"mx-1 text-[11px] text-black/15\" aria-hidden=\"true\">|</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"font-body text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wider transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded px-0.5 text-ink/35 hover:text-ink\" aria-pressed=\"false\">EN</button><span class=\"mx-1 text-[11px] text-black/15\" aria-hidden=\"true\">|</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"font-body text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wider transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded px-0.5 text-ink/35 hover:text-ink\" aria-pressed=\"false\">PT</button></span></div><a class=\"btn-primary text-xs py-2 px-4\" href=\"/fr/contact\">Demander une offre</a></li></ul></nav></div></header><main><section class=\"relative bg-navy overflow-hidden pt-36 pb-16 sm:pt-48 sm:pb-20\"><div class=\"hero-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.025]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"container-main relative z-10\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-body text-xs text-white/40 hover:text-white/65 transition-colors duration-200 mb-8\" href=\"/fr\">← <!-- -->Accueil</a><span class=\"section-label text-gold/70 block\">SRD Partners Sàrl</span><h1 class=\"font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-light text-white mt-2 leading-[1.1]\">Politique de confidentialité</h1></div></section><main class=\"bg-cream py-20 sm:py-28\"><div class=\"container-main max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none font-body text-ink\"><p class=\"text-muted text-sm mb-12\">Dernière mise à jour : mars 2026 · Conformément à la loi fédérale sur la protection des données (nLPD / révisée)</p><section class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4\">1. Responsable du traitement</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed\">Le responsable du traitement des données personnelles collectées via ce site est :</p><div class=\"mt-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-primary-100 text-sm\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">SRD Partners Sàrl</p><p class=\"text-muted mt-1\">Les Vernets 2</p><p class=\"text-muted\">2035 Corcelles NE</p><p class=\"text-muted mt-2\"><a href=\"mailto:cremilde.hirschi@srdpartners.ch\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">cremilde.hirschi@srdpartners.ch</a></p><p class=\"text-muted\"><a href=\"tel:+41328572419\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">+41 32 857 24 19</a></p></div></section><section class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4\">2. Données personnelles collectées</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4\">Nous collectons uniquement les données que vous nous transmettez volontairement via le formulaire de contact :</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-muted text-sm\"><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Nom et prénom</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Adresse e-mail</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Numéro de téléphone (optionnel)</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Nom de la société (optionnel)</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Contenu du message</li></ul><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed mt-4\">Ces données sont utilisées exclusivement pour répondre à votre demande. Aucune donnée n&#x27;est transmise à des tiers à des fins commerciales.</p></section><section class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4\">3. Finalités du traitement</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed\">Les données collectées sont traitées dans le but de :</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-muted text-sm mt-4\"><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Répondre à vos demandes d&#x27;information ou de devis</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Établir une relation contractuelle le cas échéant</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Respecter nos obligations légales en tant que cabinet fiduciaire</li></ul><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed mt-4\">La base légale du traitement est votre consentement (art. 6 al. 6 nLPD) ainsi que nos intérêts légitimes à répondre aux demandes clients.</p></section><section class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4\">4. Durée de conservation</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed\">Les données personnelles issues du formulaire de contact sont conservées pendant une durée maximale de <strong class=\"text-navy\">12 mois</strong> à compter de la dernière interaction, sauf obligation légale de conservation plus longue (notamment en matière comptable et fiscale : 10 ans conformément au Code des obligations suisse).</p></section><section class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4\">5. Vos droits</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4\">Conformément à la nLPD, vous disposez des droits suivants concernant vos données personnelles :</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-muted text-sm\"><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Droit d&#x27;accès à vos données</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Droit de rectification</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Droit à l&#x27;effacement (« droit à l&#x27;oubli »)</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Droit à la portabilité des données</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Droit d&#x27;opposition au traitement</li><li class=\"flex gap-3\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1\">→</span> Droit de retirer votre consentement à tout moment</li></ul><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed mt-4\">Pour exercer vos droits, contactez-nous à l&#x27;adresse :<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:cremilde.hirschi@srdpartners.ch\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">cremilde.hirschi@srdpartners.ch</a></p></section><section class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4\">6. Sécurité des données</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed\">Nous prenons les mesures techniques et organisationnelles appropriées pour protéger vos données personnelles contre tout accès non autorisé, modification, divulgation ou destruction. Le site est servi en HTTPS et les transmissions sont chiffrées.</p></section><section class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4\">7. Cookies</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed\">Ce site utilise uniquement des cookies techniques strictement nécessaires à son fonctionnement (langue sélectionnée). Aucun cookie publicitaire ou de tracking tiers n&#x27;est utilisé.</p></section><section class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4\">8. Contact — Responsable de la protection des données</h2><p class=\"text-muted leading-relaxed\">Pour toute question relative à la protection de vos données ou pour exercer vos droits, adressez votre demande à :</p><div class=\"mt-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border border-primary-100 text-sm\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-navy\">Cremilde Hirschi</p><p class=\"text-muted mt-1\">SRD Partners Sàrl</p><p class=\"text-muted\">Les Vernets 2<!-- -->, <!-- -->2035 Corcelles NE</p><p class=\"text-muted mt-2\"><a href=\"mailto:cremilde.hirschi@srdpartners.ch\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">cremilde.hirschi@srdpartners.ch</a></p></div><p class=\"text-muted text-sm mt-4\">Vous avez également le droit de déposer une plainte auprès du Préposé fédéral à la protection des données et à la transparence (PFPDT) :<!-- --> <span class=\"text-navy\">www.edoeb.admin.ch</span></p></section></div></div></main><footer><div class=\"h-[3px] bg-gold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"bg-navy\"><div class=\"container-main pt-14 pb-10 lg:pt-16 lg:pb-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col gap-5\"><a class=\"inline-flex self-start rounded-lg focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" aria-label=\"SRD Partners Sàrl\" href=\"/fr\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg px-3 py-2\"><img alt=\"SRD Partners Sàrl\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-10 w-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></a><p class=\"font-body text-[0.8rem] text-white/45 leading-relaxed max-w-[220px]\">Cabinet fiduciaire indépendant · Romandie</p></di